#\\\|CE747MC6WI6KVLSBMYF7ND3SD2KVPDGIPAPFDNBCG3RLZ5SZ3VU \ / AMOS7 \ YOURUM ::
#\[7]5MIYNUFNGTSTI4U2T2NNIV3NXZRHVJFBKFD3RKGTFF6KS64OIIBI 7  DATA SIGNATURE ::
#:::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::
